<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘有点头晕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她一直转来转去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>整个世界都反过来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26877</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皮特不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26878</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘发出尖叫声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31551</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只叫做布只的棕色大虫抓住了她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不敢相信我这么幸运。”布只说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在回家的路上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“回家晚了的话我的姐姐们会担心的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他有六条腿，其中的两条腿缠在拇指姑娘的腰上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不好了。”拇指姑娘小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇，这个东西真漂亮！”布只说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只鸟肯定是想吃了它，鸟都很不干净。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他的话真多。”拇指姑娘小声地自言自语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后布只停在了一个高高的树枝上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我饿了。”布只说，他黑黑的大眼睛看着拇指姑娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让我看看可以找到什么吃的东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布只展开翅膀，然后嗡嗡地飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在就是我逃走的好机会。”拇指姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她往下看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>往下跳的话太高了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然她听到了很吵的嗡嗡的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘捂住了她的耳朵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两只很大的虫子停在了树枝上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们和布只长得一模一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布只在哪里？”其中一只问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不用管他。”另一只说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们树上的那个东西在做什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走近拇指姑娘，看着她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，布只回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正嚼一片橡树叶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布只娜！布中娜！我回来了！”布只说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你去哪里了？”布中娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你给我们带晚餐回来了吗？”布只娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有这是什么？”他们指着拇指姑娘一同问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189565</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不漂亮吗？”布只骄傲地说，“是我找到的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布只娜和布中娜盯着拇指姑娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有翅膀。”布中娜吸了吸鼻子，“怎么飞呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220430</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有大眼睛。”布只娜皱了皱眉，“怎么能看得清楚呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布知没有自信了，又看了看拇指姑娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是很漂亮。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的姐姐们都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“头很小。”其中一个说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只有两条腿。”另外一只说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，我知道你们的意思。”布只点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布只，别管那个东西吧。”布中娜说，“你又不能留着它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去找吃的东西吧。”布只娜说，“我饿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布只的姐姐们飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好意思。”拇指姑娘清了清喉咙说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“会说话！”布只大声说，他非常惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘大声地叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，我会说话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你刚才太没有礼貌了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道你不能留着我的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道。那再见了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布只准备飞走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等一下！”拇指姑娘说，“你不能就这样把我留在这里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布只耸了耸肩，把拇指姑娘放在了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把她放在一朵菊花上，然后嗡嗡地飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只剩下拇指姑娘一个人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>